spec_data.Name: yum-plugin-auto-update-debug-info
spec_data.Description:
This plugin looks to see if any debuginfo packages are installed, and if there
are it enables all debuginfo repositories that are "children" of enabled
repositories.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:03:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Yum plugin to enable automatic updates to installed debuginfo packages
